WEBVTT

00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:12.560
It can be hard to put faith in something you cannot see, but real faith is not blind.

00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:23.800
Real faith is based on facts, on realities, on truth.

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:33.009
It gives us courage and strength and it helps us to endure.

00:00:33.009 --> 00:00:37.539
When life gets hard, it provides peace.

00:00:37.539 --> 00:00:45.979
It reminds us of our purpose and it brings us real joy.

00:00:45.979 --> 00:00:51.060
And how to build and strengthen your faith at the 2021 Powerful By Faith Convention

00:00:51.060 --> 00:00:52.179
of Jehovah's Witnesses.
